sourcesContent: // ejected using 'npx eject-keycloak-page' import { clsx } from "keycloakify/tools/clsx"; import type { PageProps } from "keycloakify/login/pages/PageProps"; import { useGetClassName } from "keycloakify/login/lib/useGetClassName"; import type { KcContext } from "../kcContext"; import type { I18n } from "../i18n"; export default function Register(props: PageProps, I18n>) { const { kcContext, i18n, doUseDefaultCss, Template, classes } = props; const { getClassName } = useGetClassName({ doUseDefaultCss, classes }); const { url, messagesPerField, register, realm, passwordRequired, recaptchaRequired, recaptchaSiteKey } = kcContext; const { msg, msgStr } = i18n; return ( ); }
